Data.jsonData: {"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"I’m so hungry... Is there any cake left?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/portrait_jimi_angry","talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Dad ate everything again, that pig."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Well, no choice, I’ll have to make some more. There should be ingredients downstairs."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Well, this should work. Off to the <color={color_success}>oven</color>!"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Bake at 180 degrees for 30 minutes... I really don’t have time for this nonsense."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"According to my calculations, if I cook it at 324,000 degrees, it will be done in one second."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"I’m really a genius."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Oh no... Dad's going to kill me."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Jimi...<waitSec=0.8> Wake up."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Wake up, Jimi."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"…"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Ngh...<waitSec=0.8> Five more minutes."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Jimi..."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"…."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"OH<waitSec=0.6> WAKE UP!"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"What?!"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Oh,<waitSec=0.4> what the hell is going on?"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Listen to me, Jimi...<waitSec=0.8> You’ve really made a huge mistake."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"What do you mean?"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"But really, a HUGE<waitSec=0.2> mistake."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"What did I do?"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Like if there was a world record for the biggest idiot,<waitSec=0.4> you’d be number one."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"…"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Honestly<waitSec=0.4>, I don’t know how you can look at yourself in the mi-<skipLine>"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Oh, come on! Tell me what I did or I’m going back to sleep."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Alright,<waitSec=0.3> I’m being harsh…<waitSec=0.8> Let’s get straight to the point."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"You destroyed the world.<waitSec=0.3> And it’s up to you to save it."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"…Yeah<waitSec=0.1> nah<waitSec=0.2>, I don’t have time for that."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Zzzz"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"…"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"I guess you don't really want your cake after all?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Cake?! Where?"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Calm down. I know where it is."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Well, great,<waitSec=0.3> give it to me then."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"I’d love to,<waitSec=0.5> but I can’t really."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Why?"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Your cake is in another world.<waitSec=0.3> Without it<waitSec=0.3>, your world is lost."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Wait, repeat<waitSec=0.3>, I didn’t understand."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Your cake is in another world.<waitSec=0.3> And if you don’t get it-<skipLine>"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"What?"}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"YOUR CAKE<waitSec=0.2> IS IN<waitSec=0.2> ANOTHER WORLD-<skipLine>"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"My cake?<waitSec=0.5> Wait, start over from the beginning."}
{"talkerName":"Mysterious Voice","line":"Go away."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"NO<waitSec=0.1> WAIT!"}
